    "scope_covers_installation": false,
    "comparability_notes": "This EPD covers multiple products across five batching plants in South Australia (Dry Creek, Elizabeth, Mile End, McLaren Vale, Osborne). GWP values vary significantly by product and plant — e.g. N3220P Ref ranges from 334 (Mile End) to 349 (Elizabeth) kg CO2-eq/m3. The headline GWP reported here is for N3220P Ref (32 MPa reference mix) at Dry Creek plant (344 kg CO2-eq/m3) as a representative value. A1-A3 specific data is only 5-26% (cements were excluded from specific data in this version due to proxy dataset use). PCR 2019:14 v1.11. Modules A4, A5, B1-B7 are not declared. End-of-life results (C1-C4+D) are based on a representative mix density of 2,332 kg/m3 and must be scaled linearly for other densities. Multiple Enviro Construct low-carbon mix variants are included alongside standard reference mixes."
